h3. Summary

An app with web panel conditions:
{code}
{  
     "condition":"addon_is_licensed"
  },
  {  
     "or":[  
        {  
           "condition":"addon_property_exists",
           "params":{  
              "propertyKey":"property-key",
              "objectName":"object-name"
           },
           "invert":true
        },
        {  
           "condition":"addon_property_equal_to",
           "params":{  
              "propertyKey":"property-key",
              "objectName":"object-name",
              "value":"true"
           }
        }
     ]
  }
{code}

displays the web panel even on unlicensed app on a cloud instance. 

*Observation*
# A {color:red}503{color} is thrown and an error is displayed as such "App is not responding. Wait or Cancel?" in the issue page
# Checked UPM if the app is truly unlicensed and it is (see screenshot)
# Checked if the app property does not exist, and it does not (see screenshot). This is checked so conditions are met

*Customer Impact*: Reported 3 cloud instances affected by this issue
More details in: [DEVHELP-1416|https://ecosystem.atlassian.net/browse/DEVHELP-1416]
